subject: Football
Football (College)
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Cody Journell kicked a 17-yard field goal in overtime to give No. 16 Virginia Tech a 20-17 home victory over Georgia Tech on Monday night.
